title: Picnic Time's Caliente 771
transcripts: The Caliente by picnic time is a handy portable BBQ grill and cooler in one convenient tote. The grill comes in a durable polyester carrying tote with two insulated zipper compartments. The top compartment doubles as a water resistant cooler with a six can capacity and has a fully removable lid for easy access. The charcoal grill has a 10 inch grate providing a grilling surface of over 78 square inches and features and enameled fire bowl with chrome plated grates and grate  handle. The caliente has a handy shoulder strap and sturdy foam fitted carry handle that makes transporting a breeze. And a pocket on the cooler exterior provides extra storage. the caliente is the most compact and convenient portable grill available. it makes the perfect grill for anyone who loves to Barbecue.
